1
00:00:06,060 --> 00:00:08,340
♪The white sail came too late♪

2
00:00:09,100 --> 00:00:11,340
♪Where did he go?♪

3
00:00:12,340 --> 00:00:13,820
♪Snow veils the mountains♪

4
00:00:14,060 --> 00:00:16,340
♪Love endures beyond life and death♪

5
00:00:17,860 --> 00:00:19,580
♪A black chess piece♪

6
00:00:19,660 --> 00:00:23,140
♪Whose game did he stumble into?♪

7
00:00:23,740 --> 00:00:27,620
♪All his life, there's no escape♪

8
00:00:29,420 --> 00:00:33,340
♪In ten thousand years, what will still remain?♪

9
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:40,020
♪Will anyone still love with an unchanging heart?♪

10
00:00:40,300 --> 00:00:42,620
♪I will remember♪

11
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:46,660
♪Those days long past♪

12
00:00:47,660 --> 00:00:51,580
♪As the wind drifts with the white sail♪

13
00:00:52,220 --> 00:00:53,660
♪Ten thousand years ago♪

14
00:00:53,780 --> 00:00:57,500
♪Did you once walk this shore?♪

15
00:00:57,740 --> 00:01:02,940
♪Why can't our bond be severed in this life?♪

16
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:05,100
♪I am lost yet willing♪

17
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:09,580
♪Still I love you with a steadfast heart♪

18
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:17,100
♪Until all things fade away♪

19
00:01:23,940 --> 00:01:27,220
♪The stars will remember us♪

20
00:01:27,220 --> 00:01:28,220
[Love & Crown]

21
00:01:28,220 --> 00:01:29,980
[Adapted from the novel "My Queen" by Xie Lounan]

22
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:32,980
[Episode 8]

23
00:01:38,430 --> 00:01:40,410
All the poisons have already been destroyed.

24
00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:43,540
Why then does the Begonia Pendant still react so strangely?

25
00:01:44,950 --> 00:01:47,410
Could it be that there are still other toxins hidden within the palace?

26
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,660
Princess Ying's mind is unclear.

27
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:53,980
Her words cannot be taken as truth.

28
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,540
Your Majesty,

29
00:02:05,150 --> 00:02:05,930
Your Highness,

30
00:02:06,430 --> 00:02:07,770
I mean no disrespect.

31
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:09,290
It is by His Majesty's command.

32
00:02:09,750 --> 00:02:12,100
Should a single lamp be lit in this cold palace,

33
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:14,130
a guard's life must be taken in exchange.

34
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,610
I'm truly fearful.

35
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:43,780
Ying.

36
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:47,410
Ying.

37
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:48,540
Ying.

38
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:00,340
Ying.

39
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,660
I'm your brother.

40
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,730
I have come to see you.

41
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:09,260
Qianqing!

42
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:19,500
Come.

43
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:23,610
Ying.

44
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:25,410
It's so cold,

45
00:03:26,030 --> 00:03:28,260
remember to keep your shoes on from now on.

46
00:03:39,030 --> 00:03:39,820
Ying.

47
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,290
Stop painting.

48
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:43,940
Your brother and I have come to see you.

49
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:48,220
Ying.

50
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:51,260
I brought you osmanthus and red bean dumplings.

51
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,260
After you eat them,

52
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,690
you should go to sleep early.

53
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:01,290
How did you know I like these?

54
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:10,060
Who are you?

55
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,140
Then do you want to eat them?

56
00:04:18,510 --> 00:04:20,250
When I've killed them all,

57
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,730
then I'll eat.

58
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:23,340
Kill whom?

59
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,220
Why don't you help me,

60
00:04:48,430 --> 00:04:49,410
and kill them all?

61
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,850
Mother, this teacup is exquisite.

62
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:15,540
Fine porcelain,

63
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:16,730
so clear and delicate.

64
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:20,140
Ying's illness

65
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,730
has always come and gone.

66
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,170
After much effort to nurse her,

67
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:26,460
her confusion still outweighs her clarity.

68
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:28,490
That Xiao Huan

69
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:31,250
is determined to take our lives!

70
00:05:33,070 --> 00:05:33,850
Mother.

71
00:05:34,950 --> 00:05:36,900
Ying gave poison to the Empress,

72
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,020
and attempted to assassinate His Majesty.

73
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:40,580
She was only punished by ten days without lighting a lamp.

74
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:43,610
That punishment is already merciful enough.

75
00:05:44,310 --> 00:05:46,610
Ying has never been of sound mind.

76
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,340
But why did she become this way?

77
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,610
You know the reason well.

78
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:52,460
Had it not been for that great fire at Luling Palace back then,

79
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,100
when Xiao Huan abandoned her,

80
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:56,540
she would never have been so deeply scarred.

81
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:57,580
Then

82
00:05:57,870 --> 00:05:59,780
why did Luling Palace suddenly burn for no reason?

83
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,980
What do you mean by that?

84
00:06:03,630 --> 00:06:05,490
You are my own flesh and blood,

85
00:06:05,630 --> 00:06:07,130
the child I carried for ten months,

86
00:06:07,130 --> 00:06:09,140
born through hardship and pain.

87
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,700
Do you not know why,

88
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:13,100
or for whom, I have done all this?

89
00:06:20,430 --> 00:06:21,730
So Mother has always known

90
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:23,170
the truth behind Ying's madness,

91
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:25,020
yet chose never to tell her,

92
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,900
encouraging her instead to resent His Majesty.

93
00:06:28,190 --> 00:06:29,140
Is this, Mother,

94
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:31,460
what you call love for me and Ying?

95
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,660
So,

96
00:06:44,630 --> 00:06:46,660
it is because of your sister's matter

97
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,020
that you have borne a grudge against me all this time.

98
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,660
You were in Southern Chu for so many years,

99
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:54,410
yet not once did you send a letter home.

100
00:06:55,430 --> 00:06:57,140
Whatever I asked you to do,

101
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,610
you brushed aside carelessly,

102
00:06:58,630 --> 00:06:59,540
and even

103
00:07:00,270 --> 00:07:01,580
stood against me.

104
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,140
Mother.

105
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,050
You speak too harshly.

106
00:07:18,830 --> 00:07:19,610
Does it hurt?

107
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,340
It does not.

108
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,020
Mother,

109
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,140
please be at ease.

110
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,250
Now that I have returned,

111
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:35,410
I shall protect you and my sister with all that I am.

112
00:07:35,950 --> 00:07:37,410
I will never let either of you suffer again.

113
00:07:38,190 --> 00:07:39,580
The injustice Ying endured,

114
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,540
I will never forget.

115
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:27,580
Well?

116
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,610
Did you meet His Majesty?

117
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,460
Does that mean I can stop practicing?

118
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:32,300
Look at me,

119
00:08:32,630 --> 00:08:33,820
do I look like I've met him?

120
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:38,460
Then what should we do?

121
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:41,300
His Majesty could summon Song Lanxi at any moment.

122
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,610
He values him so highly.

123
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,960
Even if I practice until I'm perfect,

124
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,850
the moment His Majesty sees the real one, I'll be exposed.

125
00:08:47,270 --> 00:08:48,180
His Majesty

126
00:08:48,870 --> 00:08:49,980
is gravely ill now.

127
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,820
He is unlikely to grant an audience for the time being.

128
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,700
As for you,

129
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,010
put your mind to practicing your calligraphy first.

130
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:58,220
We'll talk once you've fooled the officials in the Capital.

131
00:08:58,960 --> 00:08:59,370
Come,

132
00:08:59,510 --> 00:09:00,490
show me.

133
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:07,770
Your writing

134
00:09:08,030 --> 00:09:09,460
does resemble his,

135
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:11,130
yet it still lacks spirit.

136
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:13,370
Anyone who has seen Song Lanxi's true work

137
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,820
will see through it at a glance.

138
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,490
Song Lanxi

139
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:19,580
is a master of calligraphy.

140
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:22,490
A four chi scroll of his sells for more than a hundred liang of silver.

141
00:09:23,030 --> 00:09:25,340
How could that be copied so easily?

142
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,420
At the start, you insisted

143
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,370
on accompanying me to the Capital.

144
00:09:31,630 --> 00:09:32,530
You boasted

145
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:35,420
as if nothing were beyond your ability.

146
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:38,180
I said I wished to go to the Capital with you,

147
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:40,650
but did I say I meant to impersonate Song Lanxi?

148
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,300
If you think my writing is poor,

149
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,180
do it yourself if you can.

150
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,650
This robe of mine

151
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,300
is

152
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,490
suited to the Dragon Boat Festival season.

153
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,300
It is costly and difficult to make, you...

154
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:54,820
What now?

155
00:10:03,870 --> 00:10:05,010
- What are you doing? - Do not move.

156
00:10:09,780 --> 00:10:11,220
[Turtle]

157
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,890
Do not be angry, Your Highness.

158
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:14,770
Please look.

159
00:10:14,870 --> 00:10:16,460
This is the character I have practiced for over a month,

160
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,580
the one that most resembles his writing.

161
00:10:18,020 --> 00:10:18,870
[Turtle]

162
00:10:18,870 --> 00:10:19,340
Here.

163
00:10:22,780 --> 00:10:24,500
[Turtle]

164
00:10:25,980 --> 00:10:27,580
[Turtle]

165
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:34,850
Characters like this,

166
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:35,980
how many can you write?

167
00:10:37,030 --> 00:10:38,700
I can write

168
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,180
not many.

169
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,370
About two hundred or so...

170
00:10:42,390 --> 00:10:43,370
Two hundred or so?

171
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:45,820
Come,

172
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:47,130
write them all for me.

173
00:10:48,510 --> 00:10:49,300
Quickly.

174
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:49,980
Sit.

175
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,130
Come,

176
00:10:51,790 --> 00:10:52,250
write.

177
00:10:59,750 --> 00:11:01,460
Your Highness, you're blocking the light.

178
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:12,180
I can't have anyone standing here when I'm writing.

179
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:15,580
Fine.

180
00:11:20,510 --> 00:11:21,300
Hurry and write.

181
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,650
For the Grand Tutor's kindness to me,

182
00:11:31,910 --> 00:11:32,980
I would give my body and soul,

183
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,100
and repay it fully.

184
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,490
At the palace examination,

185
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,250
I will

186
00:11:38,270 --> 00:11:39,420
take first place.

187
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,060
Good.

188
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,130
You may go.

189
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,340
Well?

190
00:11:49,870 --> 00:11:51,300
Any word of Cangcang?

191
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:54,060
She claimed she was going to the Summer Palace,

192
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,420
but went to the Sword Cottage instead.

193
00:12:00,150 --> 00:12:01,300
It seems

194
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:04,180
her visit to the Sword Cottage isn't simple.

195
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,770
Then Father means...

196
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,650
Regarding Li Lu's death,

197
00:12:13,510 --> 00:12:15,340
she has never let it go.

198
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:20,820
How is the truth

199
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:23,690
she seeks coming along?

200
00:13:03,170 --> 00:13:03,990
Master.

201
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,430
I miss you.

202
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:09,580
The longer I stay in the palace,

203
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:13,300
the more I miss the carefree days I had here.

204
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,490
But you're gone.

205
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:19,940
Xiao Huan won't even give me a reason.

206
00:13:21,790 --> 00:13:22,700
Master,

207
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,420
what exactly were you all hiding from me?

208
00:13:28,270 --> 00:13:29,420
The imperial family is heartless,

209
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:31,010
yet Xiao Huan keeps helping me.

210
00:13:31,390 --> 00:13:33,060
Why is that?

211
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:36,490
Why did you kill my master?

212
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,610
I promised him

213
00:13:40,390 --> 00:13:41,700
I wouldn't tell you.

214
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:48,610
What did you say?

215
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:55,250
What aren't you allowed to tell me?

216
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:02,460
What are you all hiding from me?

217
00:14:21,150 --> 00:14:22,490
You're back, little glutton.

218
00:14:24,390 --> 00:14:25,340
What do you want to eat?

219
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:26,770
I will make it for you.

220
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,580
Master, is it ready?

221
00:14:37,270 --> 00:14:39,340
What gift are you giving me?

222
00:14:41,790 --> 00:14:43,300
You may open your eyes now.

223
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:48,890
What a beautiful pendant.

224
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:51,250
This is a protector I give you.

225
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:53,250
You must keep it with you from now on.

226
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,220
Well?

227
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,100
Do you like it?

228
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,130
I do.

229
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:58,850
Father never remembers my birthday.

230
00:14:59,150 --> 00:15:01,100
Master is much better than Father.

231
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:02,180
Thank you, Master.

232
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,490
I really like it.

233
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:04,890
As long as you like it.

234
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:10,820
Master,

235
00:15:13,150 --> 00:15:14,730
can you tell me

236
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:19,100
why Xiao Huan

237
00:15:21,150 --> 00:15:22,580
had to kill you?

238
00:15:26,750 --> 00:15:27,300
Who?

239
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:31,650
Luo.

240
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,010
Cangcang.

241
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:44,490
Speak.

242
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,250
Why are you here?

243
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:50,100
I came to pay my respects too,

244
00:15:50,790 --> 00:15:51,770
to share a drink with him.

245
00:15:58,240 --> 00:16:01,580
But Master never drank Bamboo Leaf Green.

246
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:09,370
Are you really here to pay respects?

247
00:16:18,910 --> 00:16:19,700
Cangcang,

248
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:21,370
Father

249
00:16:22,910 --> 00:16:23,980
was worried about you.

250
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:32,370
Luo,

251
00:16:34,390 --> 00:16:36,420
do you still remember this pendant?

252
00:16:37,150 --> 00:16:38,700
This Begonia Pendant

253
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,770
was given to me by Master.

254
00:16:44,910 --> 00:16:46,250
He said it would keep me safe.

255
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:56,730
I remember.

256
00:16:58,790 --> 00:17:00,490
I only learned recently

257
00:17:01,030 --> 00:17:03,300
that it is a treasure beyond price.

258
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,050
With it on me,

259
00:17:06,540 --> 00:17:08,990
no poison can get close.

260
00:17:12,110 --> 00:17:14,010
Master was protecting me all along.

261
00:17:19,590 --> 00:17:22,140
But I do not even know why he died.

262
00:17:28,670 --> 00:17:30,930
I do not even know why he died!

263
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:33,780
Am I that useless?

264
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:43,730
Cang...

265
00:17:55,470 --> 00:17:56,060
Cangcang.

266
00:18:05,430 --> 00:18:06,900
I remember when I was little,

267
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:10,780
I loved leaning against this forge.

268
00:18:11,750 --> 00:18:13,380
No matter how cold it was outside,

269
00:18:14,190 --> 00:18:15,860
it was always warm here.

270
00:18:52,510 --> 00:18:53,820
Tell me,

271
00:18:56,230 --> 00:18:58,250
when have you ever approached me

272
00:19:00,080 --> 00:19:01,380
without a purpose?

273
00:19:04,320 --> 00:19:05,340
No, My Lady.

274
00:19:05,990 --> 00:19:06,930
It was Father...

275
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:09,250
Master forged the Rex Sword for you

276
00:19:10,840 --> 00:19:13,930
and you used that very sword to kill him.

277
00:19:15,710 --> 00:19:17,780
- How am I supposed to trust you again? - I...

278
00:19:20,990 --> 00:19:23,780
How am I supposed to grow old at your side,

279
00:19:25,120 --> 00:19:26,780
to live with you in harmony?

280
00:19:27,510 --> 00:19:28,930
Since I became empress,

281
00:19:28,950 --> 00:19:30,170
I've swallowed every grievance.

282
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:32,140
In the palace,

283
00:19:33,230 --> 00:19:35,780
there hasn't been a single day I didn't try to uncover the truth!

284
00:19:35,940 --> 00:19:38,020
♪To roam the world with a sword...♪

285
00:19:38,080 --> 00:19:39,170
Tell me the truth!

286
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:45,820
Do you want me to hate you for the rest of my life?

287
