326
00:22:46,950 --> 00:22:47,820
You drank too much last night.

327
00:22:48,750 --> 00:22:49,540
Cangcang,

328
00:22:50,030 --> 00:22:51,060
do you remember

329
00:22:51,600 --> 00:22:52,780
