330
00:22:53,800 --> 00:22:54,690
What did I say?

331
00:22:57,990 --> 00:22:58,900
You didn't say anything.

332
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:08,690
Strange,

333
00:23:09,270 --> 00:23:11,340
