334
00:23:12,320 --> 00:23:14,170
How come this morning, now that the sun is out,

335
00:23:14,190 --> 00:23:15,490
it's suddenly chilly?

336
00:23:16,710 --> 00:23:18,540
I remember there was a cellar at home once,

337
00:23:18,800 --> 00:23:19,690
just like this,

338
00:23:19,710 --> 00:23:20,900
