344
00:23:48,270 --> 00:23:48,970
Let's look.

345
00:23:59,030 --> 00:23:59,730
Cangcang.

346
00:24:05,120 --> 00:24:05,820
Try this.

347
00:24:09,510 --> 00:24:10,300
It's so cold.

348
00:24:14,510 --> 00:24:15,540
Why is the wind so strong?

349
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:17,250
Could it be

350
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:18,900
there's a cellar underneath,

351
00:24:19,880 --> 00:24:20,970
connected to Sword Cottage?

352
00:24:24,080 --> 00:24:25,010
Take out the sword.

353
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:04,650
I didn't expect Master

354
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:07,650
