355
00:25:11,990 --> 00:25:12,820
Cangcang, look.

356
00:25:14,030 --> 00:25:15,210
These belong to Tang.

357
00:25:18,640 --> 00:25:20,250
Every time I mentioned Tang,

358
00:25:21,190 --> 00:25:22,540
Master would say it was in the past.

359
00:25:25,230 --> 00:25:26,340
But in his heart,

360
00:25:27,030 --> 00:25:28,100
he never really let go.

361
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:40,690
This is...

362
00:25:49,360 --> 00:25:50,650
