363
00:25:51,510 --> 00:25:52,900
I remember how she looked,

364
00:25:53,120 --> 00:25:53,900
round-faced,

365
00:25:53,990 --> 00:25:55,010
with a mole at the corner of her mouth.

366
00:25:55,840 --> 00:25:56,860
Then this...

367
00:25:58,560 --> 00:26:00,650
How could her portrait be here with Master?

368
00:26:03,750 --> 00:26:05,170
These eyebrows and eyes,

369
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:08,490
