370
00:26:09,670 --> 00:26:10,340
Cangcang,

371
00:26:10,600 --> 00:26:11,970
let's verify this later.

372
00:26:22,560 --> 00:26:24,490
This is the Ghost King's mask.

373
00:26:24,950 --> 00:26:26,540
How could it be in your master's Sword Cottage?

374
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:36,650
This is...

375
00:26:40,190 --> 00:26:41,100
How could this be?

376
00:26:43,560 --> 00:26:44,410
How could this be?

377
00:26:45,230 --> 00:26:46,010
Cangcang,

378
00:26:46,710 --> 00:26:47,490
look at this.

